<h1 id='inpatient-admission'>Inpatient Admission</h1><h2 id='overview'>Overview</h2>
<p>Provides a means to retrieve inpatient admissions associated with active visits that meet the given request criteria.</p>
<h2 id='available-operations-for-inpatient-admission'>Available operations for Inpatient Admission</h2>
<ol>
<li><a href="#get-inpatient-admission">Get Inpatient Admission</a></li>
</ol>
